 * Tipping point - https://www.merriam-webster.com/words-at-play/origin-of-the-phrase-tipping-point

 * White trash - https://www.collinsdictionary.com/us/dictionary/english/white-trash

 * Gypped - https://www.npr.org/sections/codeswitch/2013/12/30/242429836/why-being-gypped-hurts-the-roma-more-than-it-hurts-you

 * Ghetto - https://time.com/5684505/ghetto-word-history/

 * Whitelist/Blacklist - https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC6148600/

 * Tipping point - https://bestlifeonline.com/common-phrases-racist-origins/

 * Grandfathered clause - https://www.npr.org/sections/codeswitch/2013/10/21/239081586/the-racial-history-of-the-grandfather-clause

 * Long time, no see - https://www.babbel.com/en/magazine/common-racist-words-phrases

 * Master/Slave - https://www.cnn.com/2020/07/06/us/racism-words-phrases-slavery-trnd/index.html

